---
// About Section with personal information
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 bg-dark-surface/50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
        About <span class="text-primary-400">Me</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-dark-muted max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Building the future of technology, one line of code at a time
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column - Image and Quick Stats -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Professional Photo Placeholder -->
        <div class="relative w-80 h-80 mx-auto lg:mx-0 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600/20 to-purple-600/20 border-2 border-primary-500/30 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto mb-4 bg-primary-500/30 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-primary-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 9a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6zm-7 9a7 7 0 1114 0H3z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <p class="text-dark-muted text-sm">Professional Photo</p>
              <p class="text-dark-muted text-xs">(Placeholder)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating Achievement Cards -->
        <div class="hidden lg:block">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 bg-dark-bg/90 backdrop-blur-sm border border-green-500/30 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-400">9+</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-dark-muted">Years</div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-dark-bg/90 backdrop-blur-sm border border-primary-500/30 rounded-xl p-4 text-center">
            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-400">Microsoft</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-dark-muted">Current</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column - Content -->
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Senior Software Engineer at Microsoft</h3>
          
          <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
            <p class="text-dark-muted leading-relaxed">
              Based in <span class="text-primary-400">Hyderabad, India</span>, I'm passionate about creating scalable systems and innovative AI-powered developer experiences. With over 9 years of experience in the industry, I've had the privilege of working on projects that impact millions of users worldwide.
            </p>
            
            <p class="text-dark-muted leading-relaxed">
              My journey in software engineering has taken me through various domains - from building robust backend systems to crafting intuitive user interfaces. I believe in the power of clean code, efficient algorithms, and user-centric design.
            </p>

            <p class="text-dark-muted leading-relaxed">
              When I'm not coding, you'll find me exploring the latest tech trends, contributing to open-source projects, or mentoring fellow developers. I'm always excited about the next breakthrough in technology and how we can leverage it to solve real-world problems.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Key Highlights -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">Key Highlights</h4>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 p-4 bg-dark-bg/50 rounded-xl border border-gray-800/50">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-primary-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">System Architecture</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-dark-muted">Scalable & resilient systems</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 p-4 bg-dark-bg/50 rounded-xl border border-gray-800/50">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-green-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">Team Leadership</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-dark-muted">Mentoring & collaboration</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 p-4 bg-dark-bg/50 rounded-xl border border-gray-800/50">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-purple-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-purple-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">AI & Innovation</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-dark-muted">Cutting-edge solutions</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3 p-4 bg-dark-bg/50 rounded-xl border border-gray-800/50">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-orange-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-orange-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.316 3.051a1 1 0 01.633 1.265l-4 12a1 1 0 11-1.898-.632l4-12a1 1 0 011.265-.633zM5.707 6.293a1 1 0 010 1.414L3.414 10l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414 1.414l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414l3-3a1 1 0 011.414 0zm8.586 0a1 1 0 011.414 0l3 3a1 1 0 010 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L16.586 10l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="font-semibold text-white">Full-Stack Development</div>
                <div class="text-sm text-dark-muted">End-to-end solutions</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Connect CTA -->
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/arjith-retna-srikanth-1b8b9967/" 
             target="_blank" 
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.338 16.338H13.67V12.16c0-.995-.017-2.277-1.387-2.277-1.39 0-1.601 1.086-1.601 2.207v4.248H8.014v-8.59h2.559v1.174h.037c.356-.675 1.227-1.387 2.526-1.387 2.703 0 3.203 1.778 3.203 4.092v4.711zM5.005 6.575a1.548 1.548 0 11-.003-3.096 1.548 1.548 0 01.003 3.096zm-1.337 9.763H6.34v-8.59H3.667v8.59zM17.668 1H2.328C1.595 1 1 1.581 1 2.298v15.403C1 18.418 1.595 19 2.328 19h15.34c.734 0 1.332-.582 1.332-1.299V2.298C19 1.581 18.402 1 17.668 1z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
          
          <a href="#contact" 
             class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-transparent border-2 border-primary-500 text-primary-400 hover:bg-primary-500 hover:text-white font-semibold rounded-xl transition-all duration-300">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 4.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
            </svg>
            Get In Touch
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
